            "notes": "The deck focuses on ramping up quickly to play big threats and disrupt opponents with land destruction. It utilizes cards like Exploration, Green Sun's Zenith, and Primeval Titan to accelerate mana production and put pressure on opponents early. Lumra, Bellow of the Woods is the commander that can generate value by returning lands from the graveyard to the battlefield. The deck also includes powerful lands like Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth and Maze of Ith to control the battlefield. By ramping up quickly and disrupting opponents' strategies with land destruction and big threats, the deck aims to overwhelm opponents and secure a victory in the mid to late game."
